<Layout title="Thijmen Kurk - Curriculum Vitae">
  <main class="p-10">
    <article class="prose lg:text-justify" style="margin: 0 auto">
      <h1>Thijmen J. Kurk, 27</h1>

      <p>
        <i>Software Developer & Data Scientist</i><br />
        <i class="text-gray-400">Zwolle, The Netherlands</i><br />
        <a href="mailto:thijmen@exante.ai">thijmen@exante.ai</a><br />
      </p>
      <p>Fluent languages: Dutch and English</p>
      <p>
        I am a passionate IT professional, specializing in software development
        and data analysis. With a commitment to delivering superior quality, I
        have a proven track record of rapidly learning and integrating new
        technologies into my work. My unique blend of HBO and WO education,
        coupled with my practical work experience, equips me with the ability to
        seamlessly link theoretical knowledge to practical application. Being
        aware of my youth and the endless opportunities to learn, I am excited
        to expand my knowledge and skills. I am eager to take on new challenges
        that will help me grow and develop further.
      </p>
      <hr />
      <h2>Traits and Skills</h2>
      <div
