        </li>
        <li>
          <i>2014 - 2017</i> / <strong>Bachelor HBO-ICT</strong>, 8.5<br />
          <i class="text-gray-400">University of Applied Sciences Windesheim</i>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <hr />
      <h2>Work Experience</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <i>2019 - present</i> / Co-founder & technical director @ <strong
            >Exante.ai</strong
          >
          <br />
          <i class="text-gray-400">Zwolle, The Netherlands</i><br />
          As Co-Founder and Technical Director at Exante.ai, I've led a blend of
          AI consultancy and software development, including projects like data analysis
          for solar cooling systems and an automatic student-internship allocation
          system for StageMonitor. Additionally, we've developed innovative software
          products such as GPT-Detective, a tool for detecting AI-written text. A
          detailed description of our work at Exante.ai can be found <a
            href="https://exante.ai/referenties/"
            class="inline-flex items-center mb-0"
          >
            here.
          </a>
        </li>
