          />
          <i class="text-gray-400">The Hague, The Netherlands</i><br />I
          developed a RESTful API in C#, including a query language and access
          control layer, to dynamically expose data models within a database.
        </li>
        <li>
          <i>2017 - 2017</i> / Bachelor Internship @ <strong>Körbler</strong><br
          />
          <i class="text-gray-400">Graz, Austria</i><br />Using PHP, I developed
          an API and SDK combination for Körbler that dynamically exposes their
          internal databases to third parties, a solution now actively used in
          production by both internal developers and external entities.
        </li>
